              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25052384/" class="">读伊索寓言</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mooooogumuji/" class=" " title="E l e n o r e">E l e n o r e</a>
                (壮士断腕的潇洒)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25052384">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">所以我们每一种缺陷都有补偿，吝啬说是经济，愚蠢说是城市，卑鄙说是灵活，无才便说是德。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-10 11:54</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                所以我们每一种缺陷都有补偿，吝啬说是经济，愚蠢说是城市，卑鄙说是灵活，无才便说是德。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







